lumis.report

Interface IJRDataSourceProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DailyVisitorsJRDataSourceProvider, HourlyPageCacheClearJRDataSourceProvider, HourlyVisitorsJRDataSourceProvider, InterfaceGenerationJRDataSourceProvider, RatioXmlHtmlJRDataSourceProvider, XmlGenerationJRDataSourceProvider

    public interface IJRDataSourceProvider
    Provides JRDataSource objects for reports. A custom data source provider, that implements this interface, may be specified for a report.
    Since:
    4.2.0
    Version:
